members.name: SpeechRecognitionResult.isFinal
members.description: A Boolean that states whether this result is final (true) or not (false) — if so, then this is the final time this result will be returned; if not, then this result is an interim result, and may be updated later on.

members.name: SpeechRecognitionResult.length
members.description: Returns the length of the "array" — the number of SpeechRecognitionAlternative objects contained in the result (also referred to as "n-best alternatives".)

members.name: SpeechRecognitionResult.item
members.description: A standard getter that allows SpeechRecognitionAlternative objects within the result to be accessed via array syntax.
